al.com/v1/dynamic_resize/sws_path/jdx-prod-images/7f2ac605-358f-4e28-8856-6719ca0dbbae_JDX-0x0_WEB.jpg?quality=80&amp;size=100x&amp;version=4" alt="Petrole essence carburant " title="Petrole essence carburant " class="photo-fs recent-img" /> </div> <h3 class="recent-news-title"><time>2016-02-17 - </time>Anticosti, pipelines et pétrole : la majorité sile</h3></a><a href="http://www.journaldemontreal.com/2016/02/17/largent-virtuel-vive-le-progres" class="recent-news-article opinions clearfix" ><div class="absolute-container"> <img src="http://storage.journaldemontreal.com/v1/dynamic_resize/sws_path/jdx-prod-images/858a507b-1c1c-4eca-ab8d-e9423d853321_JDX-0x0_WEB.jpg?quality=80&amp;size=100x&amp;version=4" alt="bloc epargne argent" title="bloc epargne argent" class="photo-fs recent-img" /> </div> <h3 class="recent-news-title"><time>2016-02-17 - </time>L'argent virtuel, vive le progrès?</h3></a><a href="http://www.journaldemontreal.com/2016/02/16/resident-ou-residant-la-proposition" class="recent-news-article opinions clearfix" ><div class="absolute-container"> <img src="http://storage.journaldemontreal.com/v1/dynamic_resize/sws_path/jdx-prod-images/726a0bf3-eb56-4f4a-a3bf-ae280b654d8d_JDX-0x0_WEB.jpg?quality=80&amp;size=100x&amp;version=0" alt="Les mots dits" title="Les mots dits" class="photo-fs recent-img" /> </div> <h3 class="recent-news-title"><time>2016-02-16 - </time>Résident ou résidant? La proposition </h3></a><a href="http://www.journaldemontreal.com/2016/02/16/courrier-des-lecteurs-du-17-fevrier-2016" class="recent-news-article blogues clearfix" ><div class="absolute-container"> <div class="story-section-icon no-img-placeholder"> <img src="http://storage.journaldemontreal.com/v1/jdx-prod-images/static/photo/65856f4b-3cbe-49ba-bf8e-451215d04bb6_logo_jdm_lrg_white.svg" alt="Le Journal de Montréal" type="image/svg+xml" class="svg" data-png-alt="http://storage.journaldemontreal.com/v1/jdx-prod-images/static/photo/d8b5342c-1ffe-4178-b9b1-de51f49f1fb5_logo_jdm_lrg_